               <p>First London Jury - Before Mr. Recorder.</p>
               <p>1354. 
               
                  <persName id="t18300708-95-defend704" type="defendantName">
                     WILLIAM 
                     DOWSON
                  <interp inst="t18300708-95-defend704" type="surname" value="DOWSON"></interp>
