            </rs>. Aged 16. - <rs id="t18300708-95-punish540" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18300708-95-punish540" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300708-95-defend704 t18300708-95-punish540"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
